<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-white" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 font-semibold">
      Il <strong>soggetto</strong> è la persona, l'animale o la cosa di cui si parla nella frase.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-3 font-semibold">Il soggetto:</p>

    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 ml-4">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>può precedere o seguire il predicato → <em>Il sole splende.</em> / <em>Splende il sole.</em></span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>può essere sottinteso, cioè non espresso → <em>(Noi) Mangiamo un gelato.</em></span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>è assente nel caso dei verbi impersonali → <em>Piove a dirotto.</em> / <em>Si mangia male.</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="false">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Sottolinea il soggetto <span class="inline-block w-4 h-4 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle"></span> nelle seguenti frasi. Attenzione: in una frase il soggetto è sottinteso.
    </h2>

    <!-- Color Selector (hidden for mono-color) -->
    <div class="hidden">
      <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300"
           data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox"
           data-color="blue">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Quell'automobile</span> corre troppo.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">L'opera</span> è stata valutata da un esperto.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Sabato migliorerà <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">il tempo</span>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Gli amici di Lia</span> le hanno fatto una sorpresa.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Vorrei quel cappotto blu e giallo.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Chi</span> ha mangiato i biscotti?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Qualcuno</span> è passato da qui.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Voi</span> siete gentili con me.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Scrivi il soggetto sottinteso.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Amiamo la canoa e il canottaggio. →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="noi" data-correct-answer="noi">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Avete del pane in più? →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="voi" data-correct-answer="voi">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Sei veloce come una lepre! →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="tu" data-correct-answer="tu">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Vorrei una tazza di tè. →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="io" data-correct-answer="io">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Quando tornerà? →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="lui/lei" data-correct-answer="lui/lei">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Siamo qui per lo spettacolo. →</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="noi" data-correct-answer="noi">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Indica con una X se il soggetto è sottinteso (S) o assente (A).
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200">
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-left">Frase</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-center">S</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-center">A</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">Albeggiava.</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">Volete ancora del succo?</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">In questo albergo si sta bene.</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">Arriverò in orario.</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">Fa freddo.</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3">Dove andiamo stasera?</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 text-center"></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
      Qual è il soggetto della frase seguente?
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold italic text-center">
        Il manifesto è stato realizzato da alcuni ragazzi.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="A" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Il soggetto è "alcuni ragazzi".</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="B" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Il soggetto è "il manifesto".</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="C" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Il soggetto è sottinteso.</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "182", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p182"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>

</div>
